                </p>
        <p>This test case maps to technique <html:span class="technique"><html:a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/2007/WD-WCAG20-TECHS-20070517/#G84">G84: Providing a text description when the user provides information that is not in the list of allowed values</html:a>
